entry.summary: An Air Quality Alert has been issued by the Washington Department of Ecology in Yakima for Chelan and Douglas counties until further notice. The Washington Department of Ecology has announced an Air Quality Alert for Chelan and Douglas counties, due to risk of wildfire smoke. This Air Quality alert is in effect until further notice.

entry.title: Special Weather Statement issued October 05 at 11:48PM CDT by NWS
entry.summary: ...Areas of Dense Fog Overnight... Areas of dense fog have developed over portions of northeast Iowa and extreme southwest Wisconsin. Low visibilities down to 1/2 mile or less can be expected overnight into Thursday morning, especially within river valleys near and south of Highway 18.
